OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777723866
OL,3,CTeen arrested over 'bomb hoax' after
OL,4,CPeter Kay gig evacuated
OL,6,FA teenager has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of a bomb hoax offence after
OL,8,Fcomedian Peter Kay was rushed off
OL,9,Fstage during a gig on Friday night.
OL,11,FPolice said "no items of a suspicious
OL,12,Fnature were found" after the audience
OL,13,Fat the Utilita Arena in Birmingham was
OL,14,Fevacuated on May 1.
OL,16,FThe 19-year-old man remains in
OL,17,Fcustody, West Midlands Police said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
