OL,3,CTeen arrested over 'bomb hoax' after
OL,4,CPeter Kay gig evacuated
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FKay's show had been halted after a
OL,12,F"potential suspicious bag" was found,
OL,13,Fand the venue was searched.
OL,15,F"Following searches of the Utilita
OL,16,FArena last night, no items of a
OL,17,Fsuspicious nature were found," police
OL,18,Fsaid on Saturday morning.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@ZO]
