OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777723866
OL,3,CTeen arrested over 'bomb hoax' after
OL,4,CPeter Kay gig evacuated
OL,6,F"A 19-year-old man was arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of a bomb hoax offence and
OL,8,Fremains in custody this morning as our
OL,9,Finquiries continue.
OL,11,F"We're grateful to everyone for their
OL,12,Fco-operation and understanding. As
OL,13,Falways our priority is the safety of
OL,14,Fthe public."
OL,16,FWitnesses said two members of staff
OL,17,Fcame onto the stage about 45 minutes
OL,18,Finto the performance, whispered into
OL,19,FKay's ear, and then escorted him away.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
