OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777723866
OL,3,CTeen arrested over 'bomb hoax' after
OL,4,CPeter Kay gig evacuated
OL,6,FSteve Aspinall, who was at the gig
OL,7,Fwith his wife, said the audience was
OL,8,Ftold to look for security guards and
OL,9,Flisten out for any announcements.
OL,11,F"To be honest, I thought it was part
OL,12,Fof the show at first," he told the
OL,13,FPress Association.
OL,15,F"It was a strange atmosphere, eerie,
OL,16,Fjust confused really (about) what was
OL,17,Fhappening. But it was alright and
OL,18,Feveryone was calm and left quite
OL,19,Fquickly with no panic."
