OL,3,CTeen arrested over 'bomb hoax' after
OL,4,CPeter Kay gig evacuated
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the National
OL,7,FExhibition Centre said ticket holders
OL,8,Fwill be contacted directly in due
OL,9,Fcourse.
OL,11,FOn Thursday, the UK's terror threat
OL,12,Flevel was raised to "severe" meaning a
OL,13,Fterror attack is "highly likely".
OL,15,FThe Joint Terrorism Analysis Centre
OL,16,Fannounced the decision on Thursday, a
OL,17,Fday after two Jewish men were stabbed
OL,18,Fin north London and in the wake of
OL,19,Fseveral attacks in Jewish
OL,20,Fneighbourhoods in recent weeks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
